        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "There were many beautiful maidens in the land, but they were not the cleverest. There were also many maidens who were clever enough, but they were not the fairest.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_159359_000002_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/159359/3557_159359_000002_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "So once more he felt his quest for a worthy bride had proved vain, and turned his face homeward.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_159359_000003_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/159359/3557_159359_000003_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "And they were both tired out.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_159359_000003_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/159359/3557_159359_000003_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "He got off his horse and knocked at the door.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_159359_000003_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/159359/3557_159359_000003_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "They appeared very much astonished to see such a fine, handsome young knight.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_159359_000003_000016",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/159359/3557_159359_000003_000016.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "Yes, the old folk said, they did.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_159359_000003_000017",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/159359/3557_159359_000003_000017.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "There was nobody else in the house, and there was no other house for miles and miles around.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_159359_000003_000018",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/159359/3557_159359_000003_000018.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "They got on as best they could, and managed to make a living out of their goat and their cow.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_159359_000005_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/159359/3557_159359_000005_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "Then he heard singing.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_159359_000006_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/159359/3557_159359_000006_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "And you may as well tell me the plain truth, for I am determined to learn it, one way or another.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_159359_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/159359/3557_159359_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "So then the old man made a clean breast of it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_159359_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/159359/3557_159359_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "The Prince was quite right, there was somebody else in the house-it was their daughter, in her little room up in the loft.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_159359_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/159359/3557_159359_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "He was no man eater, nor woman eater either, so far as he knew; therefore they might surely let him see the maiden.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_159359_000008_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/159359/3557_159359_000008_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "Never had he seen anything half so lovely as she was!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_159359_000008_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/159359/3557_159359_000008_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "He could not picture to himself anything more lovely. But a poor beggar maid, such as she was, he might not even dream of making his wife.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_159359_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/159359/3557_159359_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "The old King was much vexed on hearing this, but he was so certain of his son's exceeding cleverness that he had no doubt matters were exactly as the Prince represented.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_159359_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/159359/3557_159359_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "Dainty food failed to tempt his appetite, no sweet sleep came to him on his downy couch.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_159359_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/159359/3557_159359_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "At last he said to himself: \"There must be an end of this.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_159359_000014_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/159359/3557_159359_000014_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "He sent off a royal courier at once, bidding him bring back an immediate answer.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_159359_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/159359/3557_159359_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "After this the Prince could no longer doubt that she was quite as clever as he was, and now he felt bound to perform the vow that he had made, which was just what he most wished to do.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_159359_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/159359/3557_159359_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "So he rode forth with all his royal train to the cottage in the wild wood; and he told the old people that he had come to woo their daughter for his bride-if she were willing.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_159359_000015_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/159359/3557_159359_000015_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "And she was willing.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_159359_000015_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/159359/3557_159359_000015_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "The old folk were very down hearted at parting from their child, but they did not wish to stand in the way of her happiness, so they gave their consent.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_8341_000002_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/8341/3557_8341_000002_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "Well! if my glass runs low, the sands shall sparkle to the last.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_8341_000002_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/8341/3557_8341_000002_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "My soul would express, in sadness and in gloom, its forecast of the dreary Orcus.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_8341_000002_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/8341/3557_8341_000002_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "But it smiles-it assures me of deliverance.'",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_8341_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/8341/3557_8341_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "As he thus concluded his soliloquy, the Egyptian involuntarily rose.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_8341_000006_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/8341/3557_8341_000006_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "Above all, rode the cloud capped summit of the Dread Mountain, with the shadows, now dark, now light, betraying the mossy caverns and ashy rocks, which testified the past conflagrations, and might have prophesied-but man is blind-that which was to come!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_8341_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/8341/3557_8341_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "'Ho!' said he, aloud, 'I have then, another companion in these unworldly night-watches.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_8341_000009_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/8341/3557_8341_000009_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "What! doth she, too, as the credulous imagine-doth she, too, learn the lore of the great stars?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_8341_000009_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/8341/3557_8341_000009_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "Well, I must see this fellow laborer.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_8341_000011_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/8341/3557_8341_000011_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "But still, unsocial in his pleasures as in his graver pursuits, and brooking neither superior nor equal, he admitted few to his companionship, save the willing slaves of his profligacy.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_8341_000012_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/8341/3557_8341_000012_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "Kings, courtiers, and sages, all trembled before the professors of the dread science.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_8341_000015_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/8341/3557_8341_000015_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "As long as he was rich, none pried into his conduct.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_8342_000000_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/8342/3557_8342_000000_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "It was you who taught me to disdain adulation: will you unteach your pupil?'",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_8342_000003_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/8342/3557_8342_000003_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "Cabinets of gems, each cabinet itself a gem, filled up the interstices of the columns; the most precious woods lined the thresholds and composed the doors; gold and jewels seemed lavished all around.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_8342_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/8342/3557_8342_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "'But thou dost not disdain riches, O Ione! they know not what life is capable of who are not wealthy.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_8342_000013_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/8342/3557_8342_000013_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "Thus, in the land beyond the grave, are ever two impalpable and spiritual hosts-the things to be, the things that have been!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_8342_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/8342/3557_8342_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "'Wilt thou prove my knowledge, Ione, and behold the representation of thine own fate?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_8342_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/8342/3557_8342_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "'But yonder,' said he, pointing to a small building which stood at the end of the vista.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_8342_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/8342/3557_8342_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "They passed into a narrow hall, at the end of which hung a sable curtain.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_8342_000026_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/8342/3557_8342_000026_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "The Neapolitan's heart beat violently.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_8342_000029_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/8342/3557_8342_000029_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "'And thou art destined to be the bride of Arbaces.'",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_8342_000031_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/8342/3557_8342_000031_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "I adore thee!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_8342_000031_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/8342/3557_8342_000031_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "Never woman had lover so devoted-so passionate as I will be to Ione.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_8342_000031_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/8342/3557_8342_000031_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "Do not struggle in my clasp: see-I release thy hand.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_8342_000031_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/8342/3557_8342_000031_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "Take it from me if thou wilt-well be it so!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_8342_000031_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/8342/3557_8342_000031_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "Ione, tremble not, thou art my queen-my goddess-be my bride!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_8342_000031_000014",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/8342/3557_8342_000031_000014.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "Arbaces shall have no ambition, save the pride of obeying thee.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_8342_000032_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/8342/3557_8342_000032_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "But she was confused-astonished: it was some moments before she could recover the power of reply.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_8342_000033_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/8342/3557_8342_000033_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "'Rise! and if thou art serious, if thy language be in earnest...'",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_8342_000034_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/8342/3557_8342_000034_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "'If!' said he tenderly.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_8342_000040_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/8342/3557_8342_000040_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "Ione sank upon the couch, half dead with terror.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_8342_000044_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/8342/3557_8342_000044_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "'Speak!' he rather shrieked than said.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_8342_000045_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/8342/3557_8342_000045_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "'It is-it is!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_8342_000046_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/8342/3557_8342_000046_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "'And his name-it is written here-his name is Glaucus!'",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3557_8342_000048_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3557/8342/3557_8342_000048_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3557",
        "content": "'Then hear me,' said Arbaces, sinking his voice into a whisper; 'thou shalt go to thy tomb rather than to his arms!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
